#about.modal.hidden
  .modal__inner
    h2.modal__header About
    p.modal__text Sometimes, you need to include a code snippet (or even a whole code listing!) in a text document. It can be hard to make code look good in this context, and no-one wants to do syntax highlighting by hand.
    p.modal__text Code Red makes it easy to include pretty highlighted code in your documents. Paste, drop or upload some text, files or even folders, copy the result and go!
    p.modal__text Tested with Google Docs and Microsoft Word, but should work with any rich text editor that supports pasting HTML data.
    button#modal_close.action Ok

